        "gender": "",
        "description": "You are the digital ghost in the machine, a master of the Matrix who sees code where others see reality. You can subvert security systems to get your team inside, slice through firewalls to extract paydata, and turn your enemies' tech against them when things get hot. You can use a sidearm when you have to, though in a firefight, your hacks can shift the tide faster than a bullet ever could. But you're most at home in the massive sprawling hosts of the Matrix, quietly cracking encryptions and sifting through data to lift what's worth more than gold in the modern world - information.\n\nKeep in mind your Real-Time Threat Assessment (RTA) Software program - you can activate this to give yourself or any of your allies +1 Defense Score as long as their Defense Score is 3 or less. You'll just need to dedicate one of your 5 agents to each instance of the program you're running."
